Class SentenceGenerator

java.lang.Object
SentenceGenerator
public class SentenceGenerator
extends java.lang.Object
Class to represent a sentence generator, like a factory design but not quite Takes in a Grammar object, and builds a string through recursive string replacement Properties: - sentence - grammar - placeholder pattern Methods: + find placeholder from regex + build grammar queue from string + generate sentence from grammar queue + get final sentence
